<step><![CDATA[Mix together eggs, butter, sugar, vanilla estract well with a wooden spoon. It should be runny, if not add some water]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Split into two baking tins and bake for 30-35 mins at 170Â°. Don't open before at least 30 mins. Let cool for 5 mins before turning on wire racks ]]></step>
